## File overview

| File                              | Purpose                                                                                     |
| --------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `normalize-page-sections.ts`      | Primary normalizer: raw ACF REST → typed `AnySectionT[]`. All pages, posts, and services use this. |
| `normalize-post-sections.ts`      | Re-export alias of `normalizePageSections` (no separate logic).                             |
| `normalize-service-sections.ts`   | Re-export alias of `normalizePageSections` (no separate logic).                             |
| `field-mappers.ts`                | Pure helper functions for safely extracting typed values from `unknown` ACF REST shapes.    |
| `section-registry.ts`             | Maps section `type` → React component. One entry per section type.                          |
| `enrich-sections.ts`              | Async second pass: resolves relationship fields (testimonials, services, posts, case studies) and CF7 form definitions. Runs server-side after normalization. |

---

## Field mappers (`field-mappers.ts`)

Always use these — never access `row.*` directly with type assertions in the normalizer.

| Function                | Input           | Output            | Use for                                           |
| ----------------------- | --------------- | ----------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| `asString(v)`           | `unknown`       | `string`          | Plain text fields, select values                  |
| `asHtml(v)`             | `unknown`       | `string`          | WYSIWYG / rich text fields (alias of asString)    |
| `asBool(v)`             | `unknown`       | `boolean`         | True/false toggles; handles `1`, `"1"`, `"yes"`, `"true"`, `"on"` |
| `asNonNegativeInt(v)`   | `unknown`       | `number`          | Number fields with a natural minimum of 0; capped at 400 by default |
| `asImage(v)`            | `unknown`       | `WpImage \| null`  | Image / gallery fields; handles URL string, id-only object, full WP media object |
| `asLink(v)`             | `unknown`       | `WpAcfLink \| null`| Link / post-object fields; handles `{ title, url, target }`, bare URL string, `href`/`URL` key variants |
| `mapCtaRepeater(rows)`  | `Array \| null`  | `CtaItem[]`        | Repeater with `cta_text` + `cta_url` rows         |
| `newSectionId()`        | —               | `string`          | Generates UUID for `id` field in `base`           |
| `asRelationshipPostIds` | `unknown`       | `number[]`        | ACF relationship fields; handles IDs, numeric strings, post objects |

