## Layout key matching — mandatory across all layers

The **exact same** `snake_case` string must appear in:
1. `acf_fc_layout` value in WordPress ACF field group
2. `PAGE_SECTION_ACF_LAYOUTS` object key
3. `case "..."` in `mapKnownPageSectionLayout()`
4. `type: "..."` literal in `AnySectionT`
5. `sectionRegistry` object key
6. `case "..."` in `SectionRenderer.tsx`
7. ACF JSON `"name"` field of the layout in `acf-import-bundle.json`

A mismatch at any point silently drops the section (no runtime error).

