## Globals (`fetch-globals.ts` / Site Options)

- **`default_cta_brand_arrow`** (image, snake or camel in REST) → `GlobalSettings.site.defaultCtaBrandArrow`. Drives the default trailing icon for all `Button` **`variant="ctaBrand"`** pills site-wide. When unset in WordPress, Next uses the built-in default URL (overridable per deploy via **`NEXT_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_CTA_BRAND_ARROW_URL`**).

